{"tid":776494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【跪低】支那儲糧油脂公司將購入7萬噸大豆並繳稅予支那政府","createTime":"2018-08-12T06:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T00:41:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"06ef0474170176d673ea3d6cb997e1342f326d18","tid":776494,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180812/large/1534051212_33c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180812%2Flarge%2F1534051212_33c4.jpg&h=0592a9e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180812/58553769\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180812%2F58553769&d=MeSrQFrfhZOm9hg6GOhevcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=fa705602\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180812%2F58553769&h=a7091d36\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180812/58553769</a><br />\n<br />\n美支貿易戰開打前，載着7萬噸大豆的美國貨輪，極速駛過黃海、渤海，希望能趕在加徵關稅前抵達遼寧大連港，但最終沒能趕上限期。一個月過去，貨輪至今仍在原地打轉，曾有傳貨主未能找到新買家，只好安排船隻在海上漂流，但據財新網報道，大豆買家支儲糧油脂公司（下稱支儲糧）近日表示，由於前期到港船隻比較集中，貨船Peak Pegasus一直在大連港口外錨排隊等待卸貨和通關，預計近日將開始卸貨，並辦理後續繳稅通關手續。<br />\n<br />\n支儲糧也表示，將按照支那國家相關法律，和已生效的對美關稅措施規定，依法繳納稅項。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》引述貨船貨主稱，Peak Pegasus於海上「打轉」，是為等待進港交貨，「由於港口倉庫容量有限，我們正在等待進港卸貨，（因）前邊還有幾艘船」。"},{"pid":"0526baa0de82ab3d7a46699b92e048043518001e","tid":776494,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:42:08.000Z","msg":"中国或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1003ef3063d58f741523b7376719e69d0b27554","tid":776494,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:48:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ffa58819302f143fcca02c249197021d1757f8b","tid":776494,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:57:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325ba0508e19ac59afa845ca3ffa14a4de2d254d","tid":776494,"uid":198175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:02:16.000Z","msg":"隻船喺公海遊咗幾十日, 終於等到大豆期貨大跌, 先至埋岸報關落貨, 關稅又俾少咗, 又贏!"},{"pid":"bb7db8e3849a3ba09f0a5c8ba5fd6ae01b38ddb9","tid":776494,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T00:28:30.000Z","msg":"收稅又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0a81ffb9f963423800f1c2016089299c352173","tid":776494,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T00:39:38.000Z","msg":"國營公司交稅俾政府，左手交右手"},{"pid":"9a0b8ece70ded22093aec0bc02abe1ad4e124498","tid":776494,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T00:40:58.000Z","msg":"之前糧倉起裳，係咪有關聯？"},{"pid":"c53b60d0b48c7655f57b8cb1cebfa21910b04832","tid":776494,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a0b8ece70ded22093aec0bc02abe1ad4e124498","tid":776494,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T00:40:58.000Z","msg":"之前糧倉起裳，係咪有關聯？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T00:41:11.000Z","msg":"火"},{"pid":"4bd87798e0042bd0e23be71917fc762fe12f68fe","tid":776494,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T00:41:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}